html:
I come from an anthill
sometimes bees come by
Sometimes a mole
Digs a hole next to it
We ants know what to do
With an ant that
Wont do what ants do
In case of an antichrist
Ants should work
Manly for the quinn
And all other ants
Isn't that is obvious
When ants get atacked
Ants fight the enemy
If they loose the fight
They simply die
title: Ants
